Class OpeningBook

  • Object
    • OpeningBook
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PolyglotBook

    public abstract class OpeningBook
extends Object
implements Closeable
    A base class for reading and selecting moves from a chess opening book. It should allow for using an alternative book once out of the main book.
    Author:
    Viktor

      • getMove

        public abstract Move getMove(Position pos,
                             OpeningBook.SelectionModel selection)
                      throws Exception
        Picks and returns an opening move for the Position0 from all the relevant entries found in the PolyGlot book based on the specified mathematical model for selection. If there have been no relevant entries found, it returns null.
        Parameters:
        pos - The position for which an opening move is sought.
        selection - The mathematical model to be applied when selecting the move.
        Returns:
        An opening move.
        Throws:
        Exception - If anything goes wrong.
